author: hwright
msg: Start writing entries information to the sqlite database.
This is part of a series of patches in progress.  It's unfinished (as expressed
by the number of TODOs) but review welcome.
(WinGeneratorBase): Include the wc-metadata sql in the list of sqlite files
(write_entry): Write the entry information to the sqlite database.
(svn_wc__entries_write): Open the sqlite database, and write entries to it.
(svn_wc__entries_init): Create the sqlite database, and write entries to it.
Add the wc.db file to the list of files in the administrative directory.
Generate the wc-metadata.sql.h file on POSIX systems.
